answer: The study of KK graviton self-interactions at a future Graviton Factory can extend our understanding of the 5-d Randall-Sundrum model by probing the accuracy of the 5-d Einstein gravity picture and yielding indirect information on the self-coupling of the 4-d graviton (hep-ph/0104199).
explanation: This paper discusses the production and self-interactions of KK gravitons at a future Graviton Factory, which can provide insights into the 5-d Randall-Sundrum model.
evidence_quote: measuring the self-interactions of these KK gravitons
